<h2>How We Test</h2>
<p>Each AI coding tool was evaluated on: code generation quality, context awareness, language support, response time, debugging capability, IDE integration depth, and overall developer experience. Tests included real-world scenarios like building full-stack applications, refactoring existing codebases, and debugging complex errors.</p>
